The gap you are getting is `ul` element default css values, which are 
```
ul {
  display: block;
  list-style-type: disc;
  margin-top: 1em;
  margin-bottom: 1 em;
  margin-left: 0;
  margin-right: 0;
  padding-left: 40px;
}
```
So to solve your problem you can update your css:
```
nav ul {
  text-align: center;
  list-style-type: none;
  margin: 0;
}
```

